  VALUES (auto_gen_id, SYS_CONTEXT ('USERENV', 'SESSION_USER'), SYSDATE, 'Route', 'INSERT', :new.Route_Number);

  VALUES (auto_gen_id, SYS_CONTEXT ('USERENV', 'SESSION_USER'), SYSDATE, 'Route', 'UPDATE', :old.Route_Number);

    IF :old.Start_Destination != :new.Start_Destination THEN
